          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " and the Stingray was born, this also gave way to younger audiences becoming infatuated with the car and so began the Corvette’s domination of the sports coupe community. Although many people remember the split window of the Stingray coupe, the example given for today’s discussion is the roadster option which combined a similar performance with the fun of a convertible.",
