          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". Of course, the owner says that he wouldn't give up his beloved Corvette for anything but it's a cool comparison. After a long life of sitting and being neglected this car has finally been brought back to life to be driven once more, we hope to see it again soon.",
